			<h3 ><a href="#p160">Re: Tea Party v. Constitution</a></h3>
			<p class="author"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=160#p160"><img src="./styles/thedruidsgrove/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=57">Tudamorf</a></strong> &raquo; Mon Nov 22, 2010 2:08 pm </p>

			

